  "translations": {
    "en": "He said: Abu al-Tayyib al-Husayn ibn Muhammad al-Nahwi, the companion of Abu Bakr Muhammad ibn al-Qasim al-Anbari, reported to me from Abu Bakr, from al-Abbas ibn al-Husayn al-Lahabi, from Ibn Hassan, from Qubaysah al-Lahabi, who said:",
    "ur": "فرمایا: ابو الطیب نے خبر دی... قبیصہ اللہبی نے کہا:",
    "tr": "İlk isnad ile Abu't-Tayyib'den... Kubaysa el-Lehebi dedi:",
    "fa": "گفت: ابوالطیب خبر داد... قبیصه لهبی گفت:",
    "id": "Dia berkata: Abu al-Tayyib mengabarkan... Qubaisah al-Lahabi berkata:",
    "bn": "তিনি বললেন: আবুত-তাইয়িব জানালেন... কুবাইসা আল-লাহাবি বললেন:",
    "es": "Dijo: Abu al-Tayyib informó... Qubaysah al-Lahabi dijo:",
    "fr": "Il dit : Abu al-Tayyib informa... Qubaysah al-Lahabi dit :",
    "de": "Er sagte: Abu al-Tayyib berichtete... Qubaysah al-Lahabi sagte:",
    "ru": "Он сказал: Абу ат-Таййиб сообщил... Кубайса аль-Лахаби сказал:",
    "zh": "他说：阿布·塔伊卜告诉我……古拜萨·拉哈比说："
  }
}